text: European Urology is a monthly peer-reviewed medical journal covering urology. It was established in 1975 and is published by Elsevier. It is the official journal of the European Association of Urology. The editor-in-chief is James Catto (University of Sheffield). According to the Journal Citation Reports, the journal had impact factor of 17.581. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Urology journals Category:Elsevier academic journals Category:Publications established in 1975 Category:Monthly journals Category:English-language journals
